{"tid":2131181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國安法竊聽監視話咁易？受害議員記者：着咩色內衣都知","createTime":"2020-07-29T16:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T05:46:12.000Z","uid":134071,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6eff6ba2825ee7ebfe4c645553bad0ce32e3e7ef","tid":2131181,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"《港區國安法》條文中截取通訊和秘密監察行動，只需特首同意便可進行。有曾於中國工作的傳媒工作者，形容被竊聽是家常便飯，有竊聽者更突然在通話插嘴「等一下，沒有（錄音）帶子」，毫不掩飾；<strong>有官員則酒後吐真言說知道女記內衣顏色，自爆監視行為。</strong>疑被竊聽多年的立法會議員陳淑莊，平日開會則以「土炮」方法希望避過監聽，不過她亦直言，面對未來截取通訊門檻更低，但「大家唔可以慣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/QIPXP6POWDRJ7NVKEYZZXD2IBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FQIPXP6POWDRJ7NVKEYZZXD2IBU%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ac2d1faf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FQIPXP6POWDRJ7NVKEYZZXD2IBU%2F&h=7bed740d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/QIPXP6POWDRJ7NVKEYZZXD2IBU/</a>"},{"pid":"8d51e1b9b87216f9e37276a2acb69e1d38aaa478","tid":2131181,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e25dd2aa3b2722f35739c691c840fd089b30a1","tid":2131181,"uid":273294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f05050252c5e0fef5994eb91f5e04ffb5e7880","tid":2131181,"uid":201359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,